### REGISTER
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@mail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### LOGIN
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@mail.com",
  "password": "newpassword123"
}

