### REFRESH СТАРЫМ ТОКЕНОМ
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "c0d27829-ad1b-48bd-9187-3592b97246fa"
}

### REFRESH ПОСЛЕ LOGOUT
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1c2VyQG1haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczNjc4OTk4LCJleHAiOjE3NzYyNzA5OTh9.qn26aTIic7vKLAykUJZiIst-Ofb0ocBSHAwGmgKzCyI"
