### Запрос на создание токена для сброса пароля
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@mail.com"
}

### Reset Password
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "4c0456a8-dc3c-4611-976d-e4602cc6fff4",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "1897231e-c73d-41a6-9790-3df734ba8fd8"
}